data.description: GORGEOUS 3 bdrm 2 bath 3 car garage home in sought after Indian Hill Heights neighborhood with many upgrades including exterior and interior paint, marble in 3 bathrooms, GRANITE countertops, stainless appliances in newly renovated kitchen and living room area,  new light fixtures, vinyl plank flooring, ANDERSON lifetime warranty windows throughout, alarm system, 2 year old roof, leaf guard gutters with warranty, new upstairs A/C heat pump unit, 2 water heaters (80gal 30gal) storage shelving in garage. Fridge, washer/dryer and chest freezer stay with home. Upstairs has separate entrance and could be easily converted into separate apartment.  BREATH-taking VIEWS of Lake on both sides of home. 4 SPACIOUS decks/balconies to enjoy outdoor living. Fire pit area patio and privacy fence in side yard.  Community civic center with events and public boat ramp. You don't want to miss what this beautiful home has to offer!! Seller will offer a 1 year home warranty at closing with purchase of home.
